    <title><![CDATA[分享几个日常用的chrome插件]]></title>
    <link href="http://wubobuaa.github.io/2015/06/26/chrome-plugins/"/>
    <id>http://wubobuaa.github.io/2015/06/26/chrome-plugins/</id>
    <published>2015-06-26T14:17:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-06-26T14:59:45.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/gighmmpiobklfepjocnamgkkbiglidom?utm_source=chrome-app-launcher-info-dialog" title="AdBlock去广告插件" target="_blank" rel="external">AdBlock</a></p>
<p>AdBlock是chrome浏览器中安装量高达4000万,几乎能够屏蔽整个互联网上的广告的一款非常著名的广告屏蔽插件。</p>
<p>2.<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/aabcgdmkeabbnleenpncegpcngjpnjkc?utm_source=chrome-app-launcher-info-dialog" title="定时刷新" target="_blank" rel="external">Easy Auto Refresh</a></p>
<p><img src="http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6941baebjw1ethvj27amvj207q042aac.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>Easy Auto Refresh可以简单的设置网页的自动刷新时间。<br><a id="more"></a><br>3.<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chklaanhfefbnpoihckbnefhakgolnmc?utm_source=chrome-app-launcher-info-dialog" title="json格式化" target="_blank" rel="external">JSONView</a></p>
<p>JSONView使JSON格式的数据有类似XML的折叠展开模式，方便检查局部数据，使JSON数据整齐格式化。</p>
<p>4.<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/hdokiejnpimakedhajhdlcegeplioahd?utm_source=chrome-app-launcher-info-dialog" target="_blank" rel="external">LastPass</a></p>
<p>5.<a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chphlpgkkbolifaimnlloiipkdnihall?utm_source=chrome-app-launcher-info-dialog" target="_blank" rel="external">OneTab</a></p>
]]></content>
